  "body": "Hi Susan,\n\nThank you for sharing the initial details regarding the team retreat proposal. I’ve reviewed the ideas and wanted to provide some thoughts and potential next steps.\n\nFirst, I think the concept of hosting the retreat at the Brighthouse Lodge sounds fantastic! The location seems perfect for encouraging team bonding and fostering creativity. However, I’d like to confirm the following details before we move forward:\n\n1. Have you finalized the dates for the retreat? It would be helpful to get feedback from the team to ensure maximum participation.\n2. Could you provide a breakdown of the estimated costs, including accommodations, meals, and any planned activities?\n3. Are there any specific goals or themes you’d like the retreat to focus on? If not, I’d be happy to brainstorm some options with you.\n\nOnce we have clarity on these items, I believe we can create a strong proposal for approval. Let me know your availability for a quick call or meeting to align on these points.\n\nLooking forward to your response!\n\nBest regards,  \nJohn Doe\n"
